<div class="text-center">
    <h1 class="display-4 mt-4"><strong>Smarter</strong> is a budget tracker for the modern age.</h1>
</div>
<div class="container h-100 mt-4" style="display: flex;">
    <div class="container-img-presentation d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" >
