    </div>
    <div class="container-text-1 col-md-6" style="width: 70%; height: 40%">
        <p>
            <h3>Why budgeting with Smarter?</h3>
        </p>
        <p>
            Yiu always know what's in your pocket. We crunch the numbers to show how much spendable money you have after setting aside enough for bills, goals and necessities.
            So you can see which expenses eat up too much of the pie.
        </p>
        <p>
            Link your banks, credit cards, loans & investment in one place, to keep track of your account balances, net worth and more.
            Smarter helps you stay on top of your bills and negotiate better rates on your cable, cell phone and other bills.
        </p>
        <p>Reach your goals easily.</p>
    </div>
</div>
